Package com.github.codeteapot.jmibeans.session

Segregation for the machine session factory and all the collaborators around it.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MachineCommand<R>
    Command to be executed remotely on a platform machine.
    MachineCommandExecution<R>
    Control of the execution of a platform machine command.
    MachineSession
    Point of interaction for a user with the system of a platform machine.
    MachineSessionAuthentication
    Authentication process for a user to establish a machine session.
    MachineSessionAuthenticationContext
    Context in which an authentication process is performed to establish a machine session.
    MachineSessionFactory
    Factory responsible for obtaining sessions established on a platform machine.
    MachineSessionFile
    Access to a remote file on a platform machine.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MachineSessionClient
    Reference implementation of a MachineSessionFactory.
    MachineSessionIdentityName
    Name of an identity.
    MachineSessionPasswordName
    Name of a password.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MachineCommandExecutionException
    Exception thrown when machine command execution has failed.
    MachineSessionException
    Exception thrown when some machine session operation fails.
